Supported platform:
	Linux
	Windows
License:
	core module:
		LGPLv2.1 or later
	others:
		GPLv3 or later

Build dependencyï¼š
	Loki:
		http://loki-lib.sourceforge.net/
	Qt >= 4.4 (with Phonon module):
		http://www.qtsoftware.com/products
	Boost C++ Libraries:
		http://www.boost.org/
	FFmpeg Libraries >= 0.5:
		http://www.ffmpeg.org/
	libFLAC >= 1.2.1:
		http://flac.sourceforge.net/
	libvorbis:
		http://www.xiph.org/downloads/
	LAME:
		http://lame.sourceforge.net/
	TagLib:
		http://developer.kde.org/~wheeler/taglib.html
On Debian-based system:
	# apt-get install libloki-dev libqt4-dev libphonon-dev libboost-dev libavcodec-dev libavformat-dev libflac-dev pkg-config libvorbis-dev libmp3lame-dev libtag1-dev

Build step:
	Linux:
		$ qmake -r
		$ make
	Windows:
		> qmake -r -tp vc

Supported formats:
	Converting:
		Depends on FFmpeg, and may extend by plugin.
		At least, wav, ape, flac, tta ... should be available.
	Playing:
		Depends on Phonon's backend.

